```

**KEY FEATURES**:
- Icons for visual identification (ðŸ’° ðŸ“‹ ðŸ¦ ðŸ“ˆ ðŸ’¸)
- Nature descriptions help users understand categories
- Parent groups filtered by nature automatically
- Validation rules documented for client-side validation
