ðŸ“± REACT NATIVE - DELETE ACCOUNT GROUP

**PURPOSE**: Delete account group with constraint validation

**DELETION CONSTRAINTS**:
1. Cannot delete if has ledger accounts (must move/delete accounts first)
2. Cannot delete if has child groups (must delete/reassign children first)

**REACT NATIVE IMPLEMENTATION**:
```typescript
const handleDelete = (groupId: number, groupName: string) => {
  Alert.alert(
    'Delete Account Group',
    `Are you sure you want to delete "${groupName}"?\n\nThis action cannot be undone.`,
    [
      {
        text: 'Cancel',
        style: 'cancel'
      },
      {
        text: 'Delete',
        style: 'destructive',
        onPress: async () => {
          try {
            await api.delete(
              `/accounting/account-groups/${groupId}`
            );

            Toast.show({
              type: 'success',
              text1: 'âœ… Deleted',
              text2: 'Account group deleted successfully'
            });

            navigation.goBack();
          } catch (error) {
            if (error.response?.status === 422) {
              // Deletion constraint error
              Alert.alert(
                'Cannot Delete',
                error.response.data.error,
                [
                  {
                    text: 'OK',
                    onPress: () => {
                      // Maybe navigate to accounts/children screen
                    }
                  }
                ]
              );
            } else {
              Toast.show({
                type: 'error',
                text1: 'Error',
                text2: error.message || 'Failed to delete'
              });
            }
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  );
};
```

**SUCCESS RESPONSE (200)**:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Account group deleted successfully"
}
```

**CONSTRAINT ERROR (422)**:
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Cannot delete account group with ledger accounts",
  "error": "This group has 5 ledger account(s). Please move or delete them first."
}
```

or

```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Cannot delete account group with child groups",
  "error": "This group has child groups. Please delete or reassign them first."
}
```

**HELPFUL UI**:
